        {
            "title": "複雜的退出:加皇資本對聯合利華食品業務重組持謹慎態度",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BTBP2jQ2dmm6IHHyY9WbKQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED1L0VO_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 加皇資本對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯合利華\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯合利華;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯合利華\">聯合利華</a>計劃中的食品業務組合重組持懷疑態度,警告稱與味好美擬議的交易引發的問題多於答案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司對聯合利華股份評級為「表現遜色」,目標價為4,200便士,並表示對目前公布的方案「不太滿意」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span>聯合利華</span></span>表示,交易可能包括157億美元的預付現金部分,其餘部分以味好美股權支付,使該公司持有新實體65%的股份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師詹姆斯·愛德華茲·瓊斯寫道,這種結構「很難算是乾淨的退出」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-162aee87-d02a-3f6e-9cef-87aca1f7f3db-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加皇資本表示,排除估計佔業務11%的印度食品部門後,好樂門和家樂等品牌約佔該部門價值的三分之二。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師表示,令人擔憂的是,聯合利華似乎正從「完全擁有權一個僅由兩個品牌主導的業務」轉向部分擁有權一個專注度低得多的業務。加皇資本寫道:「這對我們來說聽起來並不太吸引人。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司稍後的更新指出,交易條款「與預期大致相同」,聯合利華65%的股份將在股東和公司之間股份拆細,同時計劃在2029年前回購60億歐元,並實現6億美元的協同效應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,加皇資本仍「不為所動」,並補充說該交易顯示出「最低限度的控制溢價」,並讓股東持有一個複雜而龐大的食品業務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A4%87%E9%9B%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA-%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%87%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8D%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%88%A9%E8%8F%AF%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E6%8C%81%E8%AC%B9%E6%85%8E%E6%85%8B%E5%BA%A6-190115364.html",
