        {
            "title": "香港電訊減持無源網絡企 套16億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">電訊盈科（00008）及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"香港電訊\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:香港電訊;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/香港電訊\">香港電訊</a>（06823）公布，香港電訊的間接全資<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"附屬公司\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:附屬公司;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/附屬公司\">附屬公司</a>Apex Link Communications Holdings Limited以2.09億美元（約16.34億港元），向由招商局資本獨家管理及控制的Pegasus Investment BidCo Limited，出售其在目標公司Regional Link Telecom Services持有的9%股份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>出售9%股份 所得款項償債</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">出售完成後，目標公司將仍是香港電訊的間接附屬公司，亦即電訊盈科的間接附屬公司。交易所得款項將使香港電訊得以進一步加強資源，以提升及擴闊其提供予消費者的服務項目，為企業客戶提供創新及先進的技術方案，並同時改善財務狀況。款項將用作一般公司用途，包括償還債務。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e5b25501-2808-339e-9307-299c0743851a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目標公司的主要業務為投資控股。Passive Netco為目標公司的全資附屬公司，從事無源網絡業務。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2024年6月，有招商局資本背景的投資者Magic Investment Bidco Limited購入Regional Link Telecom Services的40%股權。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%8D%A8%E8%A7%92%E7%8D%B8%E5%B1%B9%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90-%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%9023%E5%84%84%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E8%9E%8D%E8%B3%87-181000151.html",
